name: Zxhrñxrl Egg Hatcher
description:
Landscape walker, the Zxhrñxrl species hatches its own kind inside the inflated back cocoon.
Filtering organic matter through allongated straw-like limbs. Parts of its own ephemeral existance consist a strong part of a greater, yet unkown eco-system.
